🌟 Exciting Announcement! 🌟

We’re thrilled to introduce Alice Guo as the speaker for our Workshop 3: VC Market Assessment. 🎙️ As the Founder of Offerversity and an Angel Investor at Cross Water Ventures, Alice will bring a wealth of experience and knowledge to our workshop.

📌 With over 12 years of international experience across the US, Canada, and China, Alice has worked at a top-tier venture capital fund (AUM $3.5B) in the US and held a management position at one of China’s largest financial institutions. She is also the co-founder of UrbanLab, China’s pioneering corporate accelerator in PropTech.

Don’t miss this opportunity to learn from a leading expert in venture capital market assessment. Join us and gain invaluable insights!
